    <text type="letter">
        <body>  
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.02915.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <note type="editorial" place="left" resp="#ht">see notes Oct 5 1890</note>
            <opener>
                <dateline> 
                    <date when="1890-10-03">October 3rd 1890.</date>
                    <name type="place"><handShift rend="printed"/>The North American Review,</name>
                    <name type="place">3 East Fourteenth Street, New York.</name>
                </dateline>
                <salute><handShift rend="manuscript"/>Dear Sir:&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Can you write a brief article for the <hi rend="underline">North American Review</hi><ptr target="loc.02915_n3"/>
                on Recent Aspects of American Literature as you have observed them? It need not be
                more than 4000 words in length&#8212;about ten pages of the 
                <hi rend="underline">Review</hi>&#8212;and in 
                return for it we should be glad to place at your
                disposal the sum of Two hundred dollars. Or possibly there is some other subject on
                which
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.02915.002.jpg" type="verso"/>
            <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.02915.003.jpg" type="recto"/>
            you would be more willing to write. In that case we trust you will allow us an
                opportunity to consider it.<ptr target="loc.02915_n2"/></p>
            <closer>
                <salute>I am, dear Sir,</salute>
                <salute>Faithfully Yours,</salute>
                <signed>William H. Rideing,</signed>
                <signed>assistant editor of the <hi rend="underline">Review.</hi></signed>
                <address>
                    <addrLine>
                        <name type="person">To Walt Whitman. Esq.</name>
                    </addrLine>
                </address> 
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.02915.004.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
    </text> 
